# CrewAI in AMP

- Build agents live in `packages/agents/amp_agents/crew_build.py` — SEO, Content, Web run with `Process.parallel`.
- LangGraph handles **intake/orchestration**; CrewAI handles **parallel creative** generation — do not duplicate orchestration in Crew tasks.
- All crew kickoffs must include `tenant_id` in task descriptions and outputs.
- Use MCP tools sparingly — register schemas in `amp_shared.mcp_rug_pull` before agent use.
- Prefer YAML-first crew definitions when scaffolding new crews; align with `crewai create crew` layout.
- Reference live docs via **crewai-docs** MCP or `https://docs.crewai.com/llms.txt` — never guess API signatures.
